{"tid":680170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙嘴酒樓男子向女食客淋腐液 至少7女受傷送院","createTime":"2018-05-27T04:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T05:20:29.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee66474d21c7e4f6f7f436caa15a4b9ff1ae0b2","tid":680170,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴區發生傷人案！今晨約11時40分，警方接報指尖沙嘴麽地道一間樓上的海鮮酒樓發生事故，有男子向在場女食客淋潑腐蝕性液體，消息稱至少有7女子被濺中受傷。警方及救護員接報正趕現場，當局至少安排多架救護車把傷者送院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180527/58243151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F58243151&d=2vFTFNp9xPePz9ek5j223wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=fa4bc0fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F58243151&h=62a8d777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180527/58243151</a>"},{"pid":"eff8af1c10f9afbc7dbaa99dfef049bcd1cb3af5","tid":680170,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"其他新聞話男子 懷疑 <br />\n妻子係女知客 同人有路"},{"pid":"8cd4156c7ea3bcbe7ac48fae9fe5ded9391d9c29","tid":680170,"uid":99493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eff8af1c10f9afbc7dbaa99dfef049bcd1cb3af5","tid":680170,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"其他新聞話男子 懷疑 <br />\n妻子係女知客 同人有路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"懷疑妻子同人有路<br />\n<br />\n個女人喺酒樓做女知客"},{"pid":"f9fcf791ee5ff9708b8d54e71b29b0eb6c8dd77e","tid":680170,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:20:29.000Z","msg":"全部女人中招"}]}